# GitLab CI/CD Files in This Project

## Main Pipeline Files
- .gitlab-ci.yml              # Full production pipeline
- .gitlab-ci-modular.yml      # Modular pipeline using includes

## CI Templates (ci-templates/)
- build.yml                   # Build stage templates
- test.yml                    # Test stage templates  
- security.yml                # Security scanning templates
- docker.yml                  # Docker build templates
- deploy-k8s.yml              # Kubernetes deployment templates
- deploy-vm.yml               # VM deployment templates

## To Use in Your Project

1. Copy .gitlab-ci.yml to your project root
2. Customize variables and stages for your needs
3. Or use modular approach with includes

## Documentation
See README.md for complete guide
